race.comment: FURIOSO RICK (1) was quickly out of the tricky draw with a fast early sectional and clocked 16.61 with a 1.5 lengths win at Healesville over 300m. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Looks the testing material. AUDACIOUS PADDY (2) was prominent throughout when winning two back but could manage only midfield last time when 6th and beaten 6 lengths at this track (26.67). Has the ability to give this a shake. BENGAL BEAST (3) used the rails draw to advantage to get home last time at this track and distance (26.28) after forging to the front and leading throughout, scoring by 1.3 lengths. Can measure up again. ZIPPING GATSBY (4) is new here but warrants respect.
